            . I am a newsman and bookseller, and live in Little Bell-alley, Coleman-street. The prisoner was in my service on the 25th of September, but I never sent him for these books, or any numbers of that work, and never had them. I turned him away on the 3d of November.</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. I was never in Mr. Burgess's shop.</p>
